* A Web Cocktail
Martini is meant to be mixed and matched. Your web app is your own!

- _Need_HTML/JSON_rendering?_ - Pull in the martini-contrib [[http://github.com/codegangsta/martini-contrib/tree/master/render][render]] package.

.code day-11-martini/render.go /START OMIT/,/END OMIT/

- _Need_gzip?_ - Go grab the martini-contrib [[http://github.com/codegangsta/martini-contrib/tree/master/gzip][gzip]] package.

.code day-11-martini/gzip.go /START OMIT/,/END OMIT/

- _Need_Sessions?_ - Confide in the martini-contrib [[http://github.com/codegangsta/martini-contrib/tree/master/sessions][sessions]] package.

.code day-11-martini/sessions.go /START OMIT/,/END OMIT/

- _Need_Form_Binding?_ - Revel in the sheer awesomeness of the martini-contrib [[http://github.com/codegangsta/martini-contrib/tree/master/binding][binding]] package.

.code day-11-martini/binding.go /START OMIT/,/END OMIT/


